title: SOS TV Walpurgis Night Fever
synopsis: Stuck on the desolate planet Walpurgis, two intrepid girls named Garnet and Crystal, along with their robotic bat Carrot, can only dispatch emergency broadcasts into space and hope that someone will eventually come to their rescue.
staff: [['Ichikawa, Kazuya', ['Director']], ['Iwanami, Yoshikazu', ['Sound Director']], ['Satomi, Tetsurou', ['Script']], ['Kaneda, Tomoko', ['Theme Song Performance']]]
